    <title>实用微分几何1</title>
    <url>/2022/08/23/DiffGeo1/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>拓扑空间，开子集，通常拓扑，连续，同胚</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h3 id="拓扑空间与开子集"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#拓扑空间与开子集"></a> 拓扑空间与开子集</h3>
<p>对某一集合<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">X</span></span></span></span>而言，我们可以通过将其某些子集<strong>指定</strong>为“开”子集，<strong>其余</strong>子集<strong>指定</strong>为非开子集的方式对X的幂集进行一个划分。</p>
<p>这等价于在<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">X</span></span></span></span>的幂集中选择一个子集<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathscr{T}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathscr" style="margin-right:0.29087em;">T</span></span></span></span></span>（将这个<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">X</span></span></span></span>幂集的子集中的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">X</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">X</span></span></span></span>的子集定义为“开”子集，其余定义为“非开”子集）。这样就定义了一个<strong>拓扑</strong><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathscr{T}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathscr" style="margin-right:0.29087em;">T</span></span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p>当然，一个幂集的子集能成为拓扑<strong>还需要满足以下三个条件</strong>：</p>
<ol>
<li><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>X</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">∅</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant="script">T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">X,\varnothing \in \mathscr{T}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8777699999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">X</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord amsrm">∅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathscr" style="margin-right:0.29087em;">T</span></span></span></span></span></li>
<li><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathscr{T}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathscr" style="margin-right:0.29087em;">T</span></span></span></span></span>对有限个元素的交封闭</li>
<li><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">T</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathscr{T}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathscr" style="margin-right:0.29087em;">T</span></span></span></span></span>对任意多个元素的并封闭</li>
</ol>
<p>对已定义某种拓扑的集合，将集合-拓扑二元组称为<strong>拓扑空间</strong>。</p>
<h3 id="通常拓扑"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#通常拓扑"></a> 通常拓扑</h3>
<p>对于度量空间可以定义<strong>开球</strong>。将以任意开球组合的并作为元素得到的拓扑为<strong>通常拓扑</strong>。这就是最常用的，在未声明情况下默认使用的拓扑。</p>
<h3 id="连续"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#连续"></a> 连续</h3>
<p>称拓扑空间之间的映射<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span></span></span></span><strong>连续</strong>，当值域的任意开集的原像（在定义域中）也总是开集。</p>
<h3 id="同胚homeomorphism"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#同胚homeomorphism"></a> 同胚homeomorphism</h3>
<p>两个拓扑空间之间存在可逆映射<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span></span></span></span>，且该映射与其逆映射都连续，则这两个拓扑空间同胚。</p>
]]></content>
